chic calderwood (1 september 1937 â€“ 12 november 1966) was a scottish light-heavyweight boxer from craigneuk in north lanarkshire, scotland who was active from 1957 to 1966. he was 6 ft. 3 in. tall and had a venomous punch, winning many of his fights by knockouts. his career was cut short when he was killed in an automobile accident.